			<div class="c-actions">
				<a href="https://tickets.edfringe.com/whats-on/craig-impossible" class="btn">Full Schedule &amp; Booking</a>
			</div>
		</div>

		<h2 id="about">About</h2>

		<div class="layout">
			<div class="layout__item  u-1/2-lap-and-up">
				[Image]
			</div><!--
			--><div class="layout__item  u-1/2-lap-and-up">
				<p class="u-color-brand  u-text-upper  u-delta">His productions are an exciting mixture of contemporary magic, psychological illusion and humour.</p>
				<p>Craig has written &amp; performed in various magic shows across the UK. furthermore In recent years he has had the opportunity to perform for audiences in Los Angeles and the Middle East.</p>
				<p>Whether an intimate parlour show for a small group or a stage production for large audiences there is always plenty of audience participation, laughter and amazing magic.</p>
				<p>His shows regularly sell out quickly so to avoid disappointment you can secure your tickets for future performances.</p>	
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="u-background-image-magic">
		<div class="wrapper">
			<h2 id="magic">Magic</h2>

			<div class="layout  u-3/5-lap-and-up">
				<div class="layout__item  u-1/2-lap-and-up">
					<h3 class="u-mb0  u-color-brand">Bar <span class="hide">Magic</span></h3>
					<p>I can join you and your friends at your home, in a bar, café or any restaurant of your choice to perform dazzling close up magic.</p>
				</div><!--
				--><div class="layout__item  u-1/2-lap-and-up">
					<h3 class="u-mb0  u-color-brand">Wedding <span class="hide">Magic</span></h3>
					<p>I am an extremely experienced wedding performer and understand how magic can add (but never distract) from the wonder of a wedding day.</p>
				</div><!--
				--><div class="layout__item  u-1/2-lap-and-up">
					<h3 class="u-mb0  u-color-brand">Stage <span class="hide">Magic</span></h3>
					<p>My stage show involves a combination of magic, mindreading and psychologicial illusion, – and always plenty of room for the most vital aspect, audience participation.</p>
				</div><!--
				--><div class="layout__item  u-1/2-lap-and-up">
					<h3 class="u-mb0  u-color-brand">Corporate <span class="hide">Magic</span></h3>
					<p>I have provided corporate entertainment for local clients such as the York Brewary to national companies such as Tesco.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="wrapper">
		<h2 id="news">News</h2>

		<div class="layout"><!--
			{% for post in posts %}
				--><div class="layout__item  u-1/3-lap-and-up  u-mb+">
					<a href="{{ post.link }}" class="c-image-overlay  c-image-overlay--reveal">
						{% if post.get_thumbnail %}
							<img src="{{ post.thumbnail.src | resize(540, 360) }}" class="c-image-overlay__img">
						{% endif %}
						<div class="c-image-overlay__body  c-image-overlay__body--bottom">
							<h3 class="[ box  box--tiny ]  u-zeta  u-background-brand-alt  u-mb0">{{ post.title }}</h3>
						</div>
					</a>
				</div><!--
			{% endfor %}
		--></div>

		<div class="c-actions">
			<a href="news/" class="btn">News Archive</a>
		</div>

		<h2 id="reviews">Reviews</h2>
